375
00:36:43.045 --> 00:36:47.870
At 20, knew already they were both technical genius and had leadership

376
00:36:47.870 --> 00:36:54.795
a，Observed real motivation: "be the richest in my scientific field while contributing most to science from industry

377
00:36:54.795 --> 00:36:59.883
