378
00:36:59.883 --> 00:37:03.983
0.7.4.3 L₃ ~30 years old.

379
00:37:03.983 --> 00:37:07.845
At 20, firmly believed they carried a grand mission

380
00:37:07.845 --> 00:37:13.570
a，Observed real motivation: "as big as possible"; expected to IPO within three years

381
00:37:13.570 --> 00:37:21.533
